The paper deals with scene text detection and recognition using deep neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The proposed model is end-to-end trainable, which is a characteristic of machine learning (cs.LG) models. The paper also mentions semantic segmentation, which is a technique used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
